If someone asks you for 100 percent up front obviously never do that.

04:31.630 --> 04:38.140
I mean that is just doesn't make sense in any scenario ever if anyone ever asked for that or more than

04:38.140 --> 04:40.710
50 percent upfront just say no.

04:40.900 --> 04:43.090
